{"tid":802320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港足球發展停滯不前原因","createTime":"2018-09-01T11:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T12:41:09.000Z","uid":195944,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f4c6e4187526aa121ec016829fd44c1f6bf723a2","tid":802320,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:27:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇電視 見到冰島政府積極推動小朋友踢足球<br />\n<br />\n當地小朋友每日只需要睇廿分鐘書就完成學業上嘅要求<br />\n<br />\n全國三十四萬人 有兩萬幾人有入球會<br />\n<br />\n全國人民休息睇波 三份一人會英雄式歡迎國家隊回國<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">踢波係一種團結國民嘅運動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前香港球迷噓蟈歌 港共政府嚇到瀨屎 <br />\n<br />\n如果全部香港球迷團結一心做某啲事情 <br />\n<br />\n你估港共 狆蟈驚唔驚？<br />\n<br />\n所以港共所有政策都不利足球發展 咩無球場呀 無人識教呀 全部都廢話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我相信 香港好快無得用 狆蟈香港依個名去參加比賽"},{"pid":"51d41388825fa422d8cd7334837c8ca1d6de54ea","tid":802320,"uid":72009,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"香港阿伯:包尾，獻世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n華人永遠功利"},{"pid":"ee144a82f91cd60bc928d9bad31771fcafc09c3c","tid":802320,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83583cd521c9dd91c491510e0d670c408f2398fb","tid":802320,"uid":34352,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"市民唔係冇心,係政府冇心<br />\n根本呢個中共政府就冇撚用"},{"pid":"11508755b2cb4438974fbee5f2668a5ada6621ee","tid":802320,"uid":125641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:38:29.000Z","msg":"香港小學生個個去補習"},{"pid":"918c8960d093f902449223cde50f99bc1be28419","tid":802320,"uid":35815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T11:39:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1951c685dfe2eb2628056bc9655f6f066869b82","tid":80232